00:00:37.391 --> 00:01:10.030 align:middle line:90%


00:01:10.030 --> 00:01:13.020 align:middle line:84%
There is something precious,
and something worth living,

00:01:13.020 --> 00:01:16.010 align:middle line:84%
and living for, and we are
here today to share that,

00:01:16.010 --> 00:01:20.130 align:middle line:84%
and to figure that out, and to
find out what it means to use

00:01:20.130 --> 00:01:22.130 align:middle line:84%
the time that we
have in the body

00:01:22.130 --> 00:01:25.090 align:middle line:84%
that we have to the
best of our abilities

00:01:25.090 --> 00:01:28.166 align:middle line:90%
to understand each other.

00:01:28.166 --> 00:01:30.586 align:middle line:84%
