00:09:43.131 --> 00:09:44.410 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:09:44.410 --> 00:09:47.390 align:middle line:84%
And now the way it works
is that militias are hired

00:09:47.390 --> 00:09:49.820 align:middle line:84%
by proxy groups, and
corporate groups,

00:09:49.820 --> 00:09:52.410 align:middle line:84%
and governments that
go into villages.

00:09:52.410 --> 00:09:57.320 align:middle line:84%
And one of their primary
methods now is mass rape.

00:09:57.320 --> 00:10:00.230 align:middle line:84%
Because it's cheap, and it's
immediate, and it's effective.

00:10:00.230 --> 00:10:02.020 align:middle line:84%
And if you rape the
women in a family,

00:10:02.020 --> 00:10:03.530 align:middle line:84%
or have the husbands
rape their daughters,

00:10:03.530 --> 00:10:05.140 align:middle line:84%
or the brothers
