00:10:05.140 --> 00:10:07.140 align:middle line:84%
you destroy the
family structure.

00:10:07.140 --> 00:10:08.350 align:middle line:90%
The family's forced to flee.

00:10:08.350 --> 00:10:11.260 align:middle line:84%
The villagers flee,and
