00:16:31.690 --> 00:16:32.550 align:middle line:90%
It's very clear.

00:16:32.550 --> 00:16:37.460 align:middle line:84%
And for many women across the
planet, who have been either

00:16:37.460 --> 00:16:42.760 align:middle line:84%
in wars like World War II, where
the comfort women, for example,

00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:45.080 align:middle line:84%
