00:17:17.180 --> 00:17:20.260 align:middle line:84%
that is really looking at root
causes-- why are so many men

00:17:20.260 --> 00:17:21.119 align:middle line:90%
raping women?

00:17:21.119 --> 00:17:24.599 align:middle line:84%
Why are so many men
