00:17:24.599 --> 00:17:25.550 align:middle line:90%
What's going on?

00:17:25.550 --> 00:17:26.940 align:middle line:84%
And so what is
that reason then?

00:17:26.940 --> 00:17:29.500 align:middle line:84%
I mean, how does the
culture of masculinity

00:17:29.500 --> 00:17:31.420 align:middle line:84%
have to be reformed,
or what needs

00:17:31.420 --> 00:17:32.680 align:middle line:90%
to take place in your opinion?

00:17:32.680 --> 00:17:34.890 align:middle line:84%
Well, I think everything about
the culture of masculinity

00:17:34.890 --> 00:17:35.860 align:middle line:90%
has to be reformed.

00:17:35.860 --> 00:17:38.730 align:middle line:84%
You know, I think the
basis of masculinity

00:17:38.730 --> 00:17:41.940 align:middle line:84%
has to do with overpowering,
and domination, and occupation.

00:17:41.940 --> 00:17:43.980 align:middle line:90%
And it's the patriarchy.

00:17:43.980 --> 00:17:45.360 align:middle line:90%
It's based on the father, right?

00:17:45.360 --> 00:17:49.570 align:middle line:84%
It's based on principles where
men need to be in charge,

00:17:49.570 --> 00:17:53.030 align:middle line:84%
and men need to
dominate, and men

00:17:53.030 --> 00:17:55.420 align:middle line:90%
insert their will on others.

00:17:55.420 --> 00:17:58.270 align:middle line:84%
And I think one of moving
things I saw with One Billion

00:17:58.270 --> 00:18:03.020 align:middle line:84%
Rising is how many men were
part of that global action,

00:18:03.020 --> 00:18:06.450 align:middle line:84%
and how many men are asserting
a different kind of masculinity

00:18:06.450 --> 00:18:09.640 align:middle line:84%
that isn't about terrorizing
and isn't about domination,

00:18:09.640 --> 00:18:11.600 align:middle line:84%
but is about tenderness, and
it's about vulnerability,

00:18:11.600 --> 00:18:13.350 align:middle line:90%
and it's about connection.

00:18:13.350 --> 00:18:15.390 align:middle line:84%
And I think the
tyranny of patriarchy

00:18:15.390 --> 00:18:18.240 align:middle line:84%
has impacted men in some ways
far worse than it has women.

00:18:18.240 --> 00:18:21.260 align:middle line:84%
It's made men divorce
themselves from their heart,

00:18:21.260 --> 00:18:23.760 align:middle line:84%
and divorce themselves
from their tears,

00:18:23.760 --> 00:18:26.810 align:middle line:84%
and divorce themselves from
questioning, and mystery,

00:18:26.810 --> 00:18:28.380 align:middle line:84%
and not knowing,
and forcing them

00:18:28.380 --> 00:18:31.290 align:middle line:84%
to know answers to questions
